4) The National Bank of the Republic of Haiti to be under the control of
                            a Board of Directors organized as follows: 


                                    Haitian
                                    American



                                    The Minister of Finance;
                                    An official to represent the holders
                                        of the bonds of 1922;



                                    An agriculturalist;
                                    An economist;



                                    A businessman;
                                    A commercial banker.



                                    A lawyer.
